{"tid":891622,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港鐵藍田站罕見意外 女學生雙腳揳月台罅隙被困","createTime":"2018-11-06T09:24:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-06T09:31:15.000Z","uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"fe24be2580b412ab6228c554d3b5e22186d6fdf1","tid":891622,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T09:24:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20181106&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=58881286\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20181106%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D58881286&d=CDdQ6ncAsjMY%2BnUCY18RJ4zZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=78f97d91\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20181106%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D58881286&h=91f46d54\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20181106&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=58881286</a><br />\n<br />\n港鐵藍田站罕見意外 <span style=\"color: red;\">女學生雙腳揳月台罅隙被困</span><br />\n<br />\n港鐵觀塘綫藍田站發生罕見意外，下午4時許，一名女學生落車步出車廂時，<span style=\"color: red;\">雙腳</span>不慎踏入月台罅隙中被困，動彈不得。車站職員及其他乘客見狀立即上前協助。消防員其後接報趕至，迅速將女學生救出，交由救護車送院檢查。<br />\n<br />\n受事件影響，涉事列車一度未能開出，往調景嶺方向的列車受阻。至下午4時38分，觀塘綫列車服務逐步回復正常。<br />\n<br />\n讀者胡先生指女同學離開車廂時，不慎將兩隻腳踏進月台及列車的罅隙，繼而仆倒在地上，不停尖叫，附近的乘客見狀，立即按動站內的緊急制，通知車站職員，車廂內所有乘客亦需落車離開。胡先生指女學生及途人嘗試用不同的方法將腳拔出，但一直未能成功，大批消防到場，驅趕在場圍觀的乘客，又嘗試用工具協助女學生將腳拔出。"},{"pid":"3f8577b599a560f8be71e8ee6ff10632c3ae3f59","tid":891622,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T09:25:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/11/06/172522_89701aba45bd7768b59eb554273580c2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F11%2F06%2F172522_89701aba45bd7768b59eb554273580c2.png&h=ca8bc062&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/11/06/172529_b31941d98426318a766400cd5ab0712c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F11%2F06%2F172529_b31941d98426318a766400cd5ab0712c.png&h=4d768abc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/11/06/172535_60fa8bc96474281047c7c95fea9bda0b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F11%2F06%2F172535_60fa8bc96474281047c7c95fea9bda0b.png&h=4faf2898&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f23f547446fc7f1da90ef19e2bb2ee1890ec042c","tid":891622,"uid":66701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T09:27:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好恐怖"},{"pid":"e396064d69d637c03202234c23297c542ef13d4b","tid":891622,"uid":65298,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T09:28:05.000Z","msg":"係咪太粗先揳住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eeb780d846f40fab91ccfe380702dd4ac4b8980e","tid":891622,"uid":67500,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T09:28:15.000Z","msg":"頭髮太厚，偷返薄少少會好modern D"},{"pid":"529357bd13f6a00833fa331e4d947747bb093aca","tid":891622,"uid":54373,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T09:28:36.000Z","msg":"任何仁呢？"},{"pid":"2cfcc1d596869363c8cc93a50890f76e37b99cc2","tid":891622,"uid":54373,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T09:31:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.1ihkg.com/540/http://img.mp.itc.cn/upload/20170328/320b29acd34942ce9dd11586a0f9e087_th.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.1ihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fimg.mp.itc.cn%2Fupload%2F20170328%2F320b29acd34942ce9dd11586a0f9e087_th.gif&h=a19e0631&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}